OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FAt least one person has been killed
OL,7,Fand nine others are missing after a
OL,8,Fmassive chemical tank holding nearly a
OL,9,Fmillion gallons of a highly corrosive
OL,10,Fliquid imploded at a facility in
OL,11,FWashington State.
OL,13,FAnother nine people were injured, some
OL,14,Fseverely, in the spill at the Nippon
OL,15,FDynawave Packaging Co., a pulp and
OL,16,Fpaper mill in Longview.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
