OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779922984
OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FOfficials have repeatedly referred to
OL,7,Fthe situation as a "recovery effort",
OL,8,Fwith Cowlitz Fire and Rescue Chief
OL,9,FScott Goldstein telling reporters on
OL,10,FTuesday: "At the moment we are not
OL,11,Faware of any rescues that are yet to
OL,12,Fbe made."
OL,14,FEmergency responders planned to work
OL,15,Fon stabilising the collapsed tank on
OL,16,FWednesday morning, which still
OL,17,Fcontained about 340,000 litres of a
OL,18,Fchemical brew known as "white liquor".
OL,19,FThey will then search for the missing.
OL,26,@rD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
