PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779922984
OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FOfficials said they would only work
OL,7,Fduring daylight hours because there
OL,8,Fwas a risk of the tank leaking more
OL,9,Fcaustic liquid and potentially
OL,10,Fcollapsing.
OL,12,F"We don't know until we know,
OL,13,Fhopefully tomorrow, how we can
OL,14,Fstabilise the tank. Do we remove the
OL,15,Fproduct first? Do we stabilise the
OL,16,Ftank first or vice versa?" Goldstein
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FAuthorities said there was no threat
OL,20,Fto the public.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
