OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779922984
OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FWhite liquor, which consists mainly of
OL,7,Fsodium hydroxide and sodium sulfide,
OL,8,Fis used with heat to break down wood
OL,9,Fto make kraft paper, a durable
OL,10,Fmaterial used in packaging, shopping
OL,11,Fbags and other products.
OL,13,FThe severity of injuries resulting
OL,14,Ffrom the spillage ranged from minor to
OL,15,Fcritical, with some suffering burns or
OL,16,Finhalation injuries, authorities said.
OL,17,FAmong those injured was a responding
OL,18,Ffirefighter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
