CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779922984
OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FGoldstein told a press conference on
OL,7,FTuesday that it was too early to
OL,8,Fdetermine the cause of the implosion.
OL,10,FWashington State Senator Patty Murray
OL,11,Fadded: "I know there's a lot of
OL,12,Fquestions about how all of this
OL,13,Fhappened and I want to assure you that
OL,14,Fwe will all continue to pressure to
OL,15,Fget answers to those questions.
OL,17,F"This community deserves that."
OL,26,@sD@HOUyD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
