OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FThe Nippon Dynawave Packaging Co.
OL,7,Ffacility remains central to the
OL,8,Fcommunity of Longview, dating back to
OL,9,F1953 and employing about 1,000 people.
OL,11,F"The people who are responders here
OL,12,Fhave friends and relatives that work
OL,13,Fon site," Goldstein noted.
OL,15,F"It is something that is impactful,
OL,16,Fand we have support networks to
OL,17,Fsupport the workers as well as the
OL,18,Femergency responders."
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@IO]wD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
