OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FThe implosion came as thousands of
OL,7,Fresidents of Southern California
OL,8,Fremained evacuated Tuesday due to a
OL,9,Fdamaged chemical tank at an aerospace
OL,10,Fplant. All evacuation orders were
OL,11,Flifted Tuesday night.
OL,13,FJust over 40 people died between
OL,14,FJanuary 2021 and mid-October 2023 as a
OL,15,Fresult of hazardous chemical
OL,16,Fincidents, according to a paper
OL,17,Freleased by a network of environmental
OL,18,Fjustice organisations in late 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
