OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779922984
OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FSafety complaints were previously
OL,7,Ffiled against Nippon Dynawave on March
OL,8,F4 and May 6.
OL,10,FThe state's labour and industries
OL,11,Fdepartment said on X that both are
OL,12,Funrelated to the current situation and
OL,13,Fremain open.
OL,15,FThe former was an anonymous complaint
OL,16,Fabout a valve on an aqua ammonia
OL,17,Fclarifier tank, according to the
OL,18,Fdepartment, which noted that "it was
OL,19,Fnot the tank that imploded".
