OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779922984
OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FNippon Dynawave, a subsidiary of Japan-
OL,7,Fbased Nippon Paper Group, has been
OL,8,Ffined a total of $3,400 (around
OL,9,F#2,500) for three separate health and
OL,10,Fsafety violations found by Washington
OL,11,FDepartment of Labour and Industries
OL,12,Finspectors since the start of 2021,
OL,13,Faccording to the department's online
OL,14,Fdatabase.
OL,16,FIn one inspection, the company was
OL,17,Fcited because face coverings were not
OL,18,Fworn by every employee when required.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
