OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779922984
OL,3,COne dead and nine missing after
OL,4,Cchemical tank implodes in Washington
OL,6,FIn another case, the inspector
OL,7,Fdetermined that an employee was
OL,8,Fexposed to the risk of falling while
OL,9,Fworking on a platform more than 4 feet
OL,10,Foff the ground.
OL,12,FIn the third incident, the department
OL,13,Fdetermined that equipment involved in
OL,14,Fa work-related accident - an amputated
OL,15,Ffinger - was moved from its original
OL,16,Fposition before the state's
OL,17,Finvestigation into the accident was
OL,18,Fcomplete.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
